Summary: The module provides a collection of diffusion pipelines for the Kandinsky generative model, covering text-to-image generation, image-to-image, inpainting, combined generation, prior embedding generation, and supporting text encoder. It integrates UNet, VQ autoencoder, multilingual CLIP, tokenizers, schedulers, and utilities for mask handling and image resizing.

Business intent: Offer developers a comprehensive set of ready-to-use pipelines to generate, edit, and manipulate images using the Kandinsky diffusion models, facilitating integration of AI-powered visual content creation into applications.

Keywords: Kandinsky, diffusion pipelines, text-to-image, image-to-image, inpainting,
